  - name: Controlling the Camera
    frenchName: 
    sentences:
    - The default camera can be controller with your mouse. Pressing and holding
      the left mouse button with accompanying mouse movement will drag the camera
      around the scene accordingly.
    - Pressing and holding the right mouse button with accompanying mouse movment
      will orbit the camera around the center of the scene.
    - Pressing and holding the LEFT shift key while scrolling the mouse wheel will
      zoom the camera in or out.
    - You may switch to different camera perspectives by clicking the button on the
      bottom left of the screen.
    - Please note that only camera 1 can be controlled as described previously. The
      remaining cameras offer stationary perspectives only.
    sentencesFR: []
